# Volumio Adaptive Themes Contributors

This project was created to solve display rotation issues on Raspberry Pi systems running Volumio.

## Project Lead

Just a Nerd

## Contributors

Contributions are welcome. Contributors will be added here as pull requests are merged.

## Based On

This project builds upon the volumio-player Plymouth theme distributed with Volumio.

## Acknowledgments

- Volumio project and community
- Plymouth development team
- Raspberry Pi Foundation

## Contributing

If you contribute to this project, please add your name or handle to this file in your pull request.
